name: 12 Issue Subscription (2 years) - receive your limited edition RUSSH tank designed by KAHLO

Subscribe to RUSSH (or extend an existing subscription) for 12 issues and not only will you always be the first to get our latest issues delivered straight to your door, plus you'll get the following bonuses:
  • receive a bonus FREE issue (13 issues for the price of 12)*
  • 25% off the cover price of 12 issues
  • enjoy your limited edition RUSSH tank designed by KAHLO valued at $109*

    •
